review_text: Parc Judith-Jasmin is a charming neighborhood public space that impresses with its beauty. There are three rocks that are placed in such a way as to convey the mystique of a Zen garden. If you are walking by or if you just need to relax, make sure to visit and relax on oen of its benches.
Such a good place to relax and take a nap while kids are playing together
